data.description: This lovely 2 bedroom, 2 full bath home is situated on a beautiful level 1+/_ acre lot with excellent proximity to local amenities.  Boasting recent renovations, this home offers a desirable neutral color scheme and also features a living room with unique beamed ceilings, LVF (Luxury Vinyl Flooring), a laundry room and a large kitchen with a breakfast area that is accented by white cabinets and stainless steel appliances.  A large open back deck and the partially covered front porch provide ample opportunities to enjoy the beauty of being outdoors.  The back yard is fenced for the safety of children and pets. This property also offers a 24x24 garage with a concrete floor.  Centrally located, this home is within a short drive to I-81 access and Tri Cities Airport. For the horse enthusiast, there is a nice boarding facility nearby!  The house was built in 1935 but all the renovations and additions were done in 2021 according to public record.
